description: Product Description Previous page Next page Multi-Purpose These gloves are ideal for hair and beauty, nail salons, tattoo artists, and beauticians. Cleaning Services A perfect gloves for professional and household cleaning, it is more comfortable for cleaning purposes. Premium Grade Nitrile Disposable Gloves Keep hands & surfaces protect by wearing these ambidextrous powder-free gloves. These gloves create a barrier between your hands and the objects you're handling, keeping your hands clean while preventing oils and dirt from transferring to surfaces. Designed for single use, they help reduce cross-contamination by being thrown away after each task. Ideal for laboratories, food service, clean rooms, and janitorial tasks, these gloves offer reliable protection in any environment. What are nitrile gloves? Nitrile gloves are disposable protective gloves made from a synthetic rubber material known as nitrile. They are widely used in various industries, including healthcare, due to their durability and protective properties. What are the advantages of using nitrile gloves? The benefits of nitrile gloves include: -High puncture resistance -Excellent chemical resistance -Latex-free, reducing the risk of allergic reactions -Good tactile sensitivity -Strong, durable, and suitable for medical use Are nitrile gloves safe for individuals with latex allergies? Yes, nitrile gloves are an ideal alternative for individuals with latex allergies. They do not contain natural rubber latex, which eliminates the risk of allergic reactions. Can nitrile gloves be reused? Nitrile gloves are typically designed for single-use. While some may remain intact after multiple uses, reuse is not recommended as it may compromise the glove's integrity, reducing its protective effectiveness. Can nitrile gloves be used for food handling? Yes, nitrile gloves are suitable for food handling, provided they are labeled as food-safe or comply with relevant food safety standards in your area.
